ActImmigration and Refugee Protection Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Immigration and Refugee Protection Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the IMMIGRATION AND REFUGEE PROTECTION REGULATIONS in order to allow the Canada Border Services Agency to pre-screen all travellers destined for Canada in order to provide board/no-board information to commercial air carriers concerning the passengers expected to be on board commercial flights prior to a flight's departure for Canada, in the context of the Interactive Advance Passenger Information initiative.
